posts.post_title: For Sale T206 Eddie Collins Old Mill Back PSA 4 (SOLDDD)
posts.post_content:
Hello all,
I've been on the wagon for a while, but wanted to get rid of one of my extras to put a couple bucks together.

Here we have a PSA 4 Eddie Collins.  This one has an Old Mill back.  It shouldn't be too tough, but it took me years to find one of these in grade while looking every week.

Priced at $235

SORRY, but the card has sold.
